Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch  Epoch Epoch from extract_bottleneck_features import *

def myResnet50_predict_breed(img_path):
    bottleneck_feature = extract_Resnet50(path_to_tensor(img_path))
    predicted_vector = my_Resnet50_model.predict(bottleneck_feature)
    predicted_index= np.argmax(predicted_vector)
    predicted_breed= dog_names[predicted_index]
    
    return predicted_breed

def image_detector(img_path):
    ifDog= dog_detector(img_path)
    ifHuman= face_detector(img_path)
    predicted_breed= myResnet50_predict_breed(img_path)
    
    img = cv2.imread(img_path)
    rgb = cv2.cvtColor(img, cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB)
    plt.imshow(rgb)
    plt.show()
    
    if (ifDog):
        return("Hello, {}".format(predicted_breed))
    elif (ifHuman):
        return("Hello, you look like a {}".format(predicted_breed))
    else:
        return("Error: nor dog or human face detected in this image!")
